https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Blake Shelton proves he is a musical force to be reckoned with in his first television special, "Blake Shelton Live: It's All About Tonight." In this 90-minute GAC exclusive presentation, the consistent hitmaker displays both his musical chops and his legendary sense of humor in the rowdy, fun-filled concert shot in Evansville, Indiana.
